In [102]:
from sklearn.metrics import classification_report, auc, roc_curve, confusion_matrix


import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

lr_fpr,lr_tpr,threshold=roc_curve(y_test,y_pred_lr_test)
lr_fpr_train,lr_tpr_train,threshold=roc_curve(y_train,y_pred_lr_train)

auc_lr=auc(lr_fpr,lr_tpr)
auc_lr_train=auc(lr_fpr_train,lr_tpr_train)

plt.figure(figsize=(10,5))
plt.plot(lr_fpr,lr_tpr,marker='.',color='red')
plt.plot(lr_fpr_train,lr_tpr_train,marker='*',color='blue')

plt.xlabel('False Positive Rate---->')
plt.ylabel('True Positive Rate---->')
Out[102]:
